AIMS OF TEACHING THE SUBJECT
•
•
•
•
To help students to appreciate the importance and the application of Chemistry in everyday life.
To assist a student to learn how to think critically in any given learning situation.
To guide a student to discover knowledge, from known to unknown, using a practical approach.
To relate and be able to apply the discovered knowledge in everyday life.
